<BaseLayout
  title="About — Vincent Del Toral"
  description="About Vincent Del Toral — software engineer with 7 years of experience, now consulting directly with businesses."
>
  <section class="section section-narrow">
    <div class="reveal">
      <h1 style="font-size: 2.4rem; margin-bottom: 32px;">About</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="about-content reveal" data-delay="100">
      <p>I build things you can point to — software that directly saves money, brings in revenue, or eliminates hours of manual work every week. Tangible problems receiving concrete solutions. That's what I do best.</p>

      <p>I've spent seven years as a software engineer across backend systems, full-stack apps, and everything in between. I got good at taking messy requirements and turning them into clean, working software — and I decided to bring that directly to business owners instead of burying it inside a large team.</p>

      <p>I work with everyone from solo founders to established businesses — technical or not. I'm happy to hop on a call, talk through what's going on, and help you figure out what makes sense to build. No jargon or pressure, just an honest conversation about your options.</p>

      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get In Touch</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
